name: Catapult - AI Version
description:
I wanted to see if it was possible to create a decent looking game using only AI art. I used my entry for a previous gamejam and had an AI make all the art, with no editing done to it. Only thing not by the AI is the background color and most of the GUI.

Hope you enjoy!

Controls:

  • Click buttons to select them
  • Click & hold left mouse to drag cat. Then drag to catapult & release.
  • Click & hold left mouse to create trampolines.

Credits:
All art by AI:

  • Midjourney
  • DALL·E 2 by OpenAI

Using prompts by me.
